def convert_base_i_to_base_10(n: str) -> list:
    ds = list(map(int, reversed(n)))
    real_part = sum(ds[::4]) + sum(ds[2::4])
    imaginary_part = sum(ds[1::4]) - sum(ds[3::4])
    return [real_part, imaginary_part]
